uint8 bit field: 0 - CO driver window active / CO driver window not active 
 1 - CO co-driver window active / CO co-driver window not active 
 2 - CO driver-side rear window active / CO driver-side rear window not active 
 3 - CO co-driver-side rear window active / CO co-driver-side rear window not active 
 4 - CO sunroof active / CO sunroof not active 
 5 - CO boot blind active / CO boot blind deactivated
